Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:21.05,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}Don't wanna die before we see our fire inside, so
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.01,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an7}(We can fight!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.89,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}泥まみれのその表情が見据えてる先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.85,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an7}(We can fly!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:32.06,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}流れ落ちる汗が全て無駄に終わるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.15,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}戦うことだけは忘れはしないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.86,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}いつでも笑える強い君の
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.36,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}泣き顔は誰も知らないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:46.58,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}心のアザは消えないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.83,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an7}(Let's go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:48.41,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an7}(Get CN - UP, get CN - UP, get CN - UP!)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.95,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}You always never gave CN - UP,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:51.08,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}You never gave CN - UP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:52.96,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}そう nothing's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.83,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}そうやってnever wake CN - UP,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.13,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}You never wake CN - UP
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}夢見て行こうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:02.34,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}いつか嘆いてた笑えない世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.47,0:20:05.26,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}どこまでも笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.18,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}そうさ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:07.56,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}Get CN - UP, get CN - UP, get CN - UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.97,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}駆け抜ければいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:34.57,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}季節が　駆けてく　息を　きらして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:41.62,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}必死に　ついてく　淡すぎる衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:48.29,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}気づけば　誰もが　顔を　変えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:55.76,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}周りを　気にして　白を黒という
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.93,0:23:02.10,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3}自分にウソはつきたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:09.06,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an8}幸せの　形は　ひとつだけじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:15.53,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an8}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.61,0:23:22.91,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an8}心に手をあてて　自分自身を今　愛してあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.16,0:23:29.38,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an8}変わる強さより　変わらない強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:36.59,CQJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be8\blur3\an8}誰かのためじゃなく　今、未来へと
